text: Mr. Pride vs Miss Prejudice () is a 2017 Chinese romantic comedy film directed by Li Haishu and Huang Yanwei and starring Dilraba Dilmurat, Leon Zhang and Vengo Gao. It was released in China on 20 April 2017. == Plot == Online writer Tang Nan Nan crosses path with Zhu Hou, a second-generation rich boy “sea turtle”, resulting in hilarious situations and face-offs. == Cast == *Dilraba Dilmurat as Tang Nan Nan *Leon Zhang as Zhu Hou *Vengo Gao as Xiao Jian Jun *Gina Jin as Mo Mo *Ma Weiwei as Editor Ma *Fan Tiantian as Da Tian Tian *Mike D.
